Interface AsyncRunner

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static interface  AsyncRunner.AsyncWork<R>

        com.google.api.core.ApiFuture<com.google.cloud.Timestamp> getCommitTimestamp()
